GET


https://serpapi.com/search.json?engine=google_autocomplete&q=pewdiepie&client=safari&hl=en&gl=us

Code to integrate


Ruby

require "serpapi" 

client = SerpApi::Client.new(
  engine: "google_autocomplete",
  q: "pewdiepie",
  client: "safari",
  hl: "en",
  gl: "us",
  api_key: "697c05cd6b6463eba244ca9769758ae5a3d4bc0e6547fc72797084d3d01665d9"
)

results = client.search
suggestions = results[:suggestions]

